<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 3: Shopping (Q4) (ID: 21)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How often do you go shopping?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> I often go shopping when i have free time for example after working hours or at the weekend.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Shopping (Q5) (ID: 22)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What kind of things do you usually buy online?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What kind of things do you usually buy online?
-> I usually buy clothes, cleaning products, anything i need. 
Why ?. 
Buying online is quicklier and the products are varying, many options. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Shopping (Q6) (ID: 23)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you prefer large malls or small local shops? Why?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer large malls or small local shops? Why?
I prefer the larger malls more. because in the big mall i can find varying products, they have a lot options to choose. I need to negotiate because every products have price tags on it. In the big mall are often equipped with air-condition so it is warm on winter and cool during the summer. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Travel (Q4) (ID: 24)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">When was the last time you went on a vacation?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> When was the last time you went on a vacation?.
Recently i had a vacation in September last year. This vocation is held by the company to help employee relax. It is employee's benefits. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Travel (Q5) (ID: 25)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you prefer traveling by car or by plane?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer traveling by car or by plane?
-> I prefer to travelling by car. because on the car, i can see the full landscape, enjoy the view and i can stop by any shops i want.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Travel (Q6) (ID: 26)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is the most important thing to consider when choosing a hotel?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the most important thing to consider when choosing a hotel ?
There are three things that i consider most when choosing a hotel.
1. the price. 
2. safety
3. locations</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Movies (Q4) (ID: 27)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How often do you go to the cinema?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How often do you go to the cinema?
-> seldom i go to the cinema. It takes me a lot of time and money. I can watch any films on TV at home. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Movies (Q5) (ID: 28)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What kind of movies do you like best?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What kind of movies do you like best ?
I love cartoon movie. On the cartoon, the charactors are unreal so i do not have to care about their personal life. With real character, sometimes, i face the articles about their dramma. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Movies (Q6) (ID: 29)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think watching movies at home is better than the theater? Why?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think watching movies at home is better than the theater? Why?
Not entirely, because watching movie at home alone is boring because i can not share my feelings about movie with anyone. Cinema can be funnier to watch with friends.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Reading (Q4) (ID: 30)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you like reading books?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like reading books?.
I am a book lover. I read book whenever i have free time at home. This is my hobby. It is relaxing.
When/where do you usually read book 

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Reading (Q5) (ID: 31)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">When do you usually read?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> When do you usually read?
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Reading (Q6) (ID: 32)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you prefer e-books or traditional paper books?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer e-books or traditional paper books?
I prefer e-book because i can read it anywherer and anytime i want. It is for free, more options to choose. I can find any e-books on the Internet. It is convinient</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Internet (Q4) (ID: 33)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How much time do you spend on the internet daily?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How much time do you spend on the internet daily?
It is about 4 to 5 hours a day. because iam an offier, my work require me to look up for information on Internet. Beside that, i also use computer for entertainment.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Internet (Q5) (ID: 34)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What do you mainly use the internet for?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What do you mainly use the internet for?
I mainly use Internet for work because it is neccessary for my jobs.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Internet (Q6) (ID: 35)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think the internet has improved our lives? Why?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think the internet has improved our lives? Why?
Yes, absolutely, beside Internet benefits, for example, i can learn on Internet, i can use it for entertainment and telephoning (get messages quickly). it also has negative side, internet waste time, it has bad information and the children should be careful with it.
 

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Sports (Q4) (ID: 36)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you play any sports?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you play any sports?
I do not play any sports because i am lazy person. If i have any free time, i would love to lie on my bed.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Sports (Q5) (ID: 37)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is a popular sport in your country?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is a popular sport in your country?
i think it is soccer. It is one of the most popular sport in Viet Nam. Vietnamese man like this. They can play well. People often stay up late to watch soccer programe. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Sports (Q6) (ID: 38)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think children should play team sports? Why?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think children should play team sports? Why?
-> I agree with that because when children take part in team sport, they can develop teamwork skills, commuciation skills and build connection with their friend. This make children become happier and better. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Music (Q4) (ID: 39)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What type of music do you listen to?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What type of music do you listen to?
-> I usually listen trendy music. I do not have any favourite artists or favourite kind of music.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Music (Q5) (ID: 40)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you play any musical instruments?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you play any musical instruments?
-> No i do not play any musical instruments because when i was i child i did not have a chance to pratice. when i grow up i do not have any free time to play this.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Music (Q6) (ID: 41)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you prefer listening to music alone or going to concerts?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer listening to music alone or going to concerts?
I prefer to listen to music alone. because it is very hot and crowded, noisy at the concert. The concert's ticket is often expensive. sometimes accidents can happen at the concert.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Hometown (Q4) (ID: 42)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Where is your hometown?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Where is your hometown?
My town is Nghe An, it is a beautiful countryside, and the local people are friendly and hospital live in neighborhood. The country is famous for it's rich culture.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Hometown (Q5) (ID: 43)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is your hometown famous for?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your hometown famous for ?/
My hometown is famous for uncle Ho village. This place is where Ho Chi Minh was born and grew up. so it is meaningful to Vietnamese people.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Hometown (Q6) (ID: 44)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Would you recommend tourists to visit your hometown?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Would you recommend tourists to visit your hometown .?
Yes, absolutely. my countryside is very lovely so i want more people to know about it.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Work (Q4) (ID: 45)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you prefer working alone or in a team?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer working alone or in a team?
I prefer to work alone but sometimes i have to work with team because with the help of my teamates i can handle jobs quickiler and more productive.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Work (Q5) (ID: 46)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What time do you usually start work?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What time do you usually start work?
i usually start work at 8.0 am every mornings from Monday to Friday. I feel very sleepy. Each morning is like a battle.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Work (Q6) (ID: 47)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is the most difficult part of your job/studies?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the most difficult part of your job/studies?
I think the most difficult part is working with other departments. because people from different department are not familiar with each other work style.  </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Transport (Q4) (ID: 48)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How do you usually get to work or school?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How do you usually get to work or school?
I usually get to work by mortorbike. because it is one of the most famous vehicle in VietNam. It is convinient and cheap.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Transport (Q5) (ID: 49)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Is public transportation convenient in your city?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is public transportation (phương tiện giao thông) convenient in your city?
I think it is not convinient because public transportations are not famous in VietNam. People have to wait for a long time. Public transportation's ticket is highly expensive  
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Transport (Q6) (ID: 50)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What can be done to reduce traffic jams?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What can be done to reduce traffic jams?
I think it is very difficult because people share the same morning routine for example the children often go to school at 7 oclock, it is also the time for the worker to go to their offices. I think the government should build bigger street and route to reduce traffic jams. the government invest more on public transportation.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Food (Q4) (ID: 51)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is your favorite dish?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite dish?
-> My favourite dish is beaf and vegetable. like beafsteak, beaf noodle, salad, ... because they are delicious and good for my health.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Food (Q5) (ID: 52)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you like cooking?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like cooking?
-> I do not like cooking. because it is time and effort demanding. After the cooking time, i often smell bad.    </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Food (Q6) (ID: 53)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you prefer eating out or eating at home? Why?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you prefer eating out or eating at home? Why?
I prefer eating at home because i know the the orgin of products so it is cleaner than eating out. eating at home is cheaper </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Friends (Q4) (ID: 54)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How often do you meet your friends?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How often do you meet your friends?
-> Very seldom, because i am growth person, i have personal life so i already busy with my jobs. We live in diferent city. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Friends (Q5) (ID: 55)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What do you usually do when you hang out?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What do you usually do when you hang out (đi chơi)?
I usually stop by the coffee shops or restaurants to have place where we meet, talk, eat with each other. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Friends (Q6) (ID: 56)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think it's important to have many friends?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think it's important to have many friends?
I dont think so, many friends are not always good. To build strong relationship, it needs time and effort. Not everyone is good to make friends. To have closed friends, you should carefully take care of the relationship.  </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Weather (Q4) (ID: 57)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What is your favorite season?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite season?
I really love auntum. I think the weather on autumn is the nicest. the leaf fall and it is often warm. It is suitable with outdoor activities. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Weather (Q5) (ID: 58)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Does the weather affect your mood?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Does the weather affect your mood?
Yes absolutely, because the good weather can make me feel more comfortable for example, in the anmtum, it is warm so it make me want to go outside more. but in the hot weather i just want to stay at home with air-condition. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Weather (Q6) (ID: 59)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What do you usually do on rainy days?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What do you usually do on rainy days?
On rainy days, i want to sleep more and sometimes i sit near the windows to see the rain. </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Health (Q4) (ID: 60)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What do you do to stay healthy?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What do you do to stay healthy?
-> I eat more vegetables.
-> I avoid staying up late.
-> sometimes i go outside to go walking or go jogging.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Health (Q5) (ID: 61)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How often do you exercise?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Health (Q6) (ID: 62)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">Do you think people today care enough about their health?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think people today care enough about their health?
-> Not entirely, because the young generation usually stay up late and the workers overtime a lot. They use too much Television, mobile. It is not good for their health</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Technology (Q4) (ID: 63)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">What electronic device do you use the most?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What electronic device do you use the most?
-> I use mobile most. because mobile is very convinient.  It is small i can bring it to anywhere. You can send the messages and calls with a mobile phone. I can find information on the Internet by mobile phone</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Technology (Q5) (ID: 64)</h3><p><div class="bg-white p-4 border rounded shadow-sm text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-700">How has technology changed your daily life?</div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How has technology changed your daily life?
Techology changed my daily life a lot. I use it for any tasks, entertainment. I can not live without it. </p><hr></body></html>